'''機載太空火箭發射'''是指从高空飛行的飞机上发射[[火箭|火箭]]，並通過火箭将卫星送入[[近地轨道|近地轨道]]。從高空飞行的飞机上发射火箭的主要优点是，火箭不需要在低空密集的[[大气层|大气层]]中飞行，因為低空密集的大气层相對於高空，存在對火箭更多的升空阻力，為克服阻力，火箭就需要更多的[[裝藥|推进剂]]，所以機載太空火箭發射能節省燃料<ref name="Sarigul-Klijn2003">{{Cite web|title=Flight Mechanics of Manned Sub-Orbital Reusable Launch Vehicles with Recommendations for Launch and Recovery|url=http://www.spacefuture.com/archive/flight_mechanics_of_manned_suborbital_reusable_launch_vehicles_with_recommendations_for_launch_and_recovery.shtml|access-date=2021-01-20|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112000850/http://www.spacefuture.com/archive/flight_mechanics_of_manned_suborbital_reusable_launch_vehicles_with_recommendations_for_launch_and_recovery.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

